rottapeli.peli

Class Settings

  • java.lang.Object
    • rottapeli.peli.Settings

  • public class Settings
extends Object
    Settings manager that can be reconfigured in the program. Settings are loaded from an external file and changed settings are saved to the external file.
    Author:
    Pavel
